manipulated_prompt_obj.inputs:
<|user|>
Write an XML document describing the release of the latest Google Pixel phone. The document must contain at least three placeholders, such as [price], and you must not use commas in your response.
<|assistant|>

raw_response_obj.response:
<|user|>
Write an XML document describing the release of the latest Google Pixel phone. The document must contain at least three placeholders, such as [price], and you must not use commas in your response.
<|assistant|>
```xml
<phoneRelease>
  <model>Google Pixel 8</model>
  <releaseDate>2023-10-31</releaseDate>
  <features>
    <camera>State of the art [cameraTechnology]</camera>
    <display>Stunning [displaySize] inch screen</display>
    <battery>Long lasting [batteryLife] hours</battery>
  </features>
  <pricing>
    <basePrice>[price]</basePrice>
    <storageOptions>Available in [storageOptions] sizes</storageOptions>
  </pricing>
  <availability>
    <regions>Available in [regions] countries</regions>
    <preOrder>Pre order starts [preOrderDate]</preOrder>
  </availability>
</phoneRelease>
```<|end_of_text|>
